        a               fabio:JournalArticle ;
        dc:creator      "Dolibaina, Diego Rodrigo" , "Casagrande, Mirna Martins" , "Dias, Fernando Maia Silva" , "Mielke, Olaf Hermann Hendrik" ;
        dc:date         "2013" ;
        dc:title        "Taxonomy of the ‘ Synargis axenus complex’ belonging to the ‘ Synargis regulus’ species group, with a phylogenetic reassessment of the genus Synargis Hübner, 1819 (Lepidoptera: Riodinidae: Nymphidiini)" ;
