<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4720313>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 17–36. Species belonging to the ‘Synargis axenus complex’ and Synargis regulus, dorsal and ventral views. 17–20, Synargis ochrophlegma stat. nov. 21–24, Synargis bifasciata. 25–28, Synargis perrupta stat. rev., typical phenotype. 29, 30, Synargis perrupta stat. rev., melanic phenotype. 31, 32, Synargis gorpa sp. nov., holotype. 33–36, Synargis regulus. Scale bar = 1 cm. Sex indicated in the figure." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4720313/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4720319>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 46–57. Male genitalia of Synargis species belonging to the ‘Synargis axenus complex’. Lateral view; tegumen and uncus in dorsal view, and eighth sternite. 46–48, Synargis ochrophlegma stat. nov. 49–51, Synargis bifasciata. 52–54, Synargis perrupta stat. rev. 55–57, Synargis gorpa sp. nov., paratype. Scale bar = 0.25 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4720319/files/figure.png" .

